Package org.jsonurl.jsonp Description

An implementation of the JSON→URL interface based on the JSON-P interface defined by JSR-374.

The primary entry point for most use cases is JsonUrlParser, which parses JSON→URL text into instances of JsonObjectBuilder and JsonArrayBuilder.

JsonUrlWriter has static methods for creating JSON→URL text from instances of JsonObjectBuilder and JsonArrayBuilder.
